  "name": "RPlog_First_Encounter",
  "title": "First Encounter in the Snow",
  "summary": "In the snow-blanketed Fountain Square of Plaxton on Caspar, the aging Imperial commander Danik Kreldin spots a wanted Jedi, Ezkhil, and his Rodian companion Gimel lurking in an alleyway and quietly comms the Conqueror to report them. Spotting the surveillance, Ezkhil confronts Danik directly while Gimel takes up a concealed firing position with a heavy blaster pistol. The standoff turns when Ezkhil seizes Danik's arm and sends searing pain through it with the Force, crippling his shooting hand. Outmatched against this unfamiliar kind of Jedi and his armed ally, Danik retreats into the crowd with a promise that they will meet again. Nearby, the heavily pregnant New Republic Ambassador Delgard departs by hired speeder, while Ezkhil rebukes Gimel for nearly opening fire, knowing the Empire now knows they have been seen.",
